.  From time to time, at Parent's request and without further consideration, the Shareholder shall cooperate with Parent and Merger Sub in making all filings and obtaining all consents of Governmental Entities and third parties and execute and deliver such additional documents and take all such further actions as may be necessary or desirable to effect the actions and consummate the transactions contemplated by this Agreement.
 
