Item 2.02
                                          
Results of Operations and Financial Condition
 
On December 19, 2012, Bed Bath & Beyond Inc. (the "Company") issued a press release announcing the Company's financial results for its fiscal third quarter ended November 24, 2012.  A copy of this press release is attached hereto as Exhibit 99.1 and is incorporated herein by reference.
 
